sources.description: Ted Weems and His Orchestra with a row of "Bathing Beauties" on the beach of Atlantic City, New Jersey performing, " Cheer Up, Good Times Are Coming " - one of the many popular, uplifting and optimistic songs that appeared after the Wall Street Crash of 1929 .
